info.description:
####
Mojo
####

Mojo is a set of django apps that can be used independantely or combined.

The list includes:

mojo-dashboard
==============

This app adds a dashboard and a menu on the default Django admin. It includes a set of default widget that track metrics about the application and can synchronize with Google Analytics to display a graphic of attendance evolution.

mojo-toolbar
============

This app manages a toolbar for admins to easily navigate to most relevant admin features, switch between backoffice and front to edit or view objects and indicate version.
